model.name: Generic genome-scale metabolic model of Homo sapiens

body.p: Genome-scale metabolic models are valuable tools to study metabolism and provide a scaffold for the integrative analysis of omics data. This is the latest version of Human-GEM, which is a genome-scale metabolic model of a generic human cell. The objective of Human-GEM is to serve as a community model for enabling integrative and mechanistic studies of human metabolism.
